â“ï¸Q5)What is a Kafka topic, and how does it function?
âœ…ï¸A topic is a logical category for messages. Producers write to topics, and consumers subscribe to them.

â“ï¸Q6)How does Kafka handle fault tolerance?
âœ…ï¸Kafka replicates partitions across multiple brokers. If a broker fails, a replica takes over, ensuring data availability

